snippet.title: Celebrity Deposition Breakdown | Justin Bieber
snippet.description:
#justinbieber​ #bieber​ #deposition​

Link to original highlight video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jGuuEHa1J2k

Speaker: Sina Rezvanpour, Esq.
Website: https://www.sinarezlaw.com/​
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/_thisisnotl...​
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/sina-rezv...​

Attorney Sina Rezvanpour, Esq. breaks down video footage from a 2014 deposition of Justin Bieber relating to a civil case against him and his bodyguard(s) brought by a photographer. 

Sina breaks down what exactly Biebz is doing right, and what he is doing wrong. Through his explanation, we learn a little bit more about the deposition process.
